          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "luxury limo was purchased by Mercury brand new and is a Mercedes-Benz fan’s dream since so many consider these second-gen S-Class models to be the best ever made. At the time, the S-Class had suddenly emerged as the sedan for the rich and famous to own, and Mercury was part of that trend.",
