        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2020/11/Motorious---6--9.jpg",
        "width": 1920,
        "height": 1080,
        "caption": "photo credit: Wikimedia Commons"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "For many, owning a Range Rover is a sign you’ve arrived financially, maybe because they’re so expensive to keep running since the luxury SUVs are ",
